description:
HOT OFF THE PRESSES, EPISODE 4!

Thanks again to everyone for giving my little videos a chance in this big YouTube full of great Crack videos, I appreciate each and every view, like, and comment I get, and if I haven't gotten around to responding to your comments I'm working my way to them!

I don't own anything in these except the time spent splicing clips and audio together.
